 preferred hard and soft skills. Example Business Administrator requirements 3-5 years of business experience Ability to occasionally travel Knowledge of company and its position in the market Basic computer skills Great interpersonal skills to work with employees Ability to work independently Business Administrator related job titles: Corporate Administrator Business Administrative Executive Business Administrative Assistant Business Manager Corporate Business Administrator Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
